			<div class="content" id="post-content-4489904">
									

<p>I don't normally write violent or grimdark fiction, but I had the idea for an atrocity Mobile Task Force, and wanted to see what happened if I wrote it. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580883830" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span> for feedback on the forums, and several others on IRC (chime in if I left you out!)</p>
<p>For more of my stuff, a lot of which is significantly more lighthearted, check out <a href="/literallymechanical-s-author-page">my Author Page</a>. I particularly recommend <a href="/scp-4357">SCP-4357</a> if you're looking for something funny.</p>

							</div>

								
