			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4489982">
									

<p>No-voting at the moment as I'm not a fan of grim-dark settings and the sort, and I much prefer my headcanon that the Foundation isn't evil, and is good at heart, albeit misguided at points.</p>
<p>To elaborate, I'm just not a fan of this kind of stuff, it's not something I'm opposed to see on the site, far from it, but it's not something I'd enjoy reading. In terms of actual writing though, I think you've done a marvelous job, it's really well done.</p>

